BOM Weather API
Weather:
ftp://ftp.bom.gov.au/anon/gen/fwo/IDN11050.xml

Trains:
https://opendata.transport.nsw.gov.au/status
http://www.sydneytrains.info/rss/feeds/trackwork.xml


Traffic disruptions:
https://www.livetraffic.com/traffic/rss/sydney.atom

Dataset explorer:
https://data.gov.au/dataset?q=sydney+traffic&sort=extras_harvest_portal+asc%2C+score+desc%2C+metadata_modified+desc

Objective:
1. Show the weather for the day. What to expect, high and low temperatures.
2. Show the UV for the day, and the protection times
3. Show the status of each train line today.
4. Expand the above with detailed information.
5. If there is upcoming trackwork show that too.
6. Show the roads status. Anything with expect delays. Can expand if needed.
7. Make this responsive


Fonts:
https://erikflowers.github.io/weather-icons/

Unsplash:
https://unsplash.com/documentation#get-a-random-photo


temp:
https://css-tricks.com/methods-contrasting-text-backgrounds/